<h2 id="conclusion">Conclusion:</h2>
<p>Its not a big deal to work with column level ACL. But its worth to test every small feature. So you have better visibility about the feature and find the bugs like what we found above. Iâ€™ll update this blog once the AWS team confirms this as a bug or not.</p>
